    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "You are a Partnership Manager at MeetGeek.\n\nClassify this partner inquiry and determine the appropriate response.\n\nINQUIRY DATA:\n- Name: {{ $json.full_name }}\n- Email: {{ $json.email }}\n- Interest: {{ $json.interest_type }}\n- Request: {{ $json.request_details }}\n- Audience Size: {{ $json.audience_size }}\n- Licenses Considered: {{ $json.licenses_considered }}\n- Additional Notes: {{ $json.additional_notes }}\n\nCLASSIFY INTO ONE OF THESE CATEGORIES:\n\n1. **BIG_DEAL** - Requires manual handling:\n   - Reseller/Distributor requests\n   - 10+ licenses\n   - Enterprise mentions\n   - Strategic partnerships\n   - Co-marketing requests\n   - Large audience (10k+)\n\n2. **STARTUP** - Auto-respond with STARTUP30 code:\n   - Startup discount requests\n   - Early-stage companies\n   - Small teams (1-5 licenses)\n\n3. **NONPROFIT** - Auto-respond with proof request:\n   - Non-profit organizations\n   - Educational institutions\n   - .edu emails\n   - Charity mentions\n\n4. **AFFILIATE** - Auto-respond with program details:\n   - Affiliate program interest\n   - Referral requests\n   - Commission mentions\n   - Content creators/influencers\n\nRULES:\n- Corporate email from known company + vague request = likely BIG_DEAL\n- If mentions \"evaluating\" or \"pilot\" = BIG_DEAL\n- When in doubt, classify as BIG_DEAL (safer to manual review)",
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "ai-classify",
      "name": "AI Agent: Classify Deal",
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent",
      "typeVersion": 1.7,
      "position": [288, 192]
    },
